**Cereal API**
A RESTful API for managing a cereal database. Built with ASP.NET Core and Entity Framework Core, this project demonstrates CRUD operations, filtering, and CSV-based data seeding.

**Features**
*Create, Read, Update, Delete cereals in database
*Filter cereals by values
*Seed database from csv file
*Driver class for testing and demonstration

**Endpoints**
POST: /api/cereals
DELETE: /api/cereals/{name}

**Dependencies**
If using Docker, dependencies can be ignored.
*SQLite
*ASP.NET core
*Entity Framework Core
*CsvHelper

**Installing**
git clone https://github.com/carolinekjaersgaard/cerealdatabase.git

**Executing Program**
Running api with docker in webserver: docker compose up --build
Running api in webserver: dotnet run
Run driver class: dotnet run -- --test

Access at: http://localhost:5250/swagger

